.vscode/

# Raw harvested asset pools (bulk, mixed-license) — NOT committed. These are the
# candidate libraries we curate kits *from*; one chosen file per voice is copied
# into public/drumkits/<kit>/ by hand.
drum-samples/
midi-library/
loops/
# NOTE: the 16 curated drumkit WAVs under public/drumkits/<kit>/ ARE committed
# (~1.1 MB total) so the sampled kits actually work on the live GitHub Pages
# deploy. Sources are credited in the README. (Previously these were ignored via
# `public/drumkits/**/*.wav`, which broke the remote deploy with 404s.)

# …but DO commit the small curated loop corpus used as test fixtures
# (the bulk loops/ above stays ignored; these are a handful for the test suite).
!test/fixtures/loops/
!test/fixtures/loops/**
music/**
